@node "Purpose" "What to do with it"

@{b}Purpose@{ub}
=======

  If you can answer the following questions with "YES",
  you need this program:

    - You have a Prelude soundcard
    - You are interested in music and sound
    - You like MUI programs

  It seems that this is your program! Now read on...


  PrlMixerMUI is a program to control the Prelude output level of each
  of the channels Line, Aux1, Aux2 and DAC. It acts like the original
  mixer, but has a MUI interface and a level display that is able to
  show the selected level in decibel.

@endnode


